    <rigor-hint>FULL</rigor-hint>
    <rigor-reason>Creates net-new component (`WorkspacePaneMenu.tsx`) plus wires it into `WorkspacePane.tsx` rightSlot. Fluent v9 Dropdown with multi-section structure (Open / Home / Switch Workspace / Edit) and dispatches into WorkspaceTabManager + WorkspaceLayoutWizard. Load-bearing for FR-12. ADR-012 (shared placement consideration), ADR-021 (Fluent v9 tokens) apply. FULL rigor with code-review + adr-check at Step 9.5.</rigor-reason>
    <parallel-group>C</parallel-group>
    <parallel-safe>false</parallel-safe>
