  <notes>
    <completion-date>2026-05-20</completion-date>
    <completion-summary>
      Created `WorkspacePaneMenu.tsx` (~470 LOC) as a Fluent v9 Menu rendered in the WorkspacePane
      PaneHeader rightSlot. Implements all four FR-12 sections with `MenuDivider` separators:
      (1) Open tabs newest-first with trailing `DismissRegular` close button on each non-Home tab;
      (2) Home pinned non-closable entry with `HomeRegular` icon, no `×`;
      (3) Switch Workspace — fetches layouts via `authenticatedFetch` (ADR-028), lists them with
          active checkmark, + "+ New Workspace" action launching the wizard;
      (4) Edit current workspace — launches the wizard in edit / saveAs mode.

      WorkspaceLayoutWizard launch uses `Xrm.Navigation.navigateTo` (pageType=webresource,
      sprk_workspacelayoutwizard) matching `LegalWorkspace/Shell/WorkspaceGrid.tsx#handleCreateLayout`.
      `templateFilter` is passed as a comma-separated query parameter; the wizard's `main.tsx` is
      plumbed (new in this task) to parse it back into `readonly LayoutTemplateId[]` and forward
      to App.tsx. SpaarkeAi consistently surfaces the 6-template subset
      (`2-col-equal,3-row-mixed,hero-2x2,sidebar-main,single-column,single-column-5`) per FR-14.

      WorkspaceTabManager wiring is via the existing `handleTabChange` / `handleTabClose`
      callbacks lifted from `WorkspacePane.tsx` — the menu is a pure consumer of the
      `{ tabs, activeTabId, onTabSelect, onTabClose }` prop contract, with no direct dependency
      on the manager class (ADR-012 separation of concerns).

      Switch Workspace selection persists the chosen layoutId in `sessionStorage`
      (`spaarke.workspace.activeLayoutId`) and dispatches a `spaarke:workspace-layout-changed`
      `CustomEvent` on `window`. The Home tab refetch wiring that consumes this signal is out of
      scope for task 032 — the contract is laid here so a follow-up task can wire it.

      Files modified:
        - NEW src/solutions/SpaarkeAi/src/components/workspace/WorkspacePaneMenu.tsx
        - MOD src/solutions/SpaarkeAi/src/components/workspace/WorkspacePane.tsx (rightSlot wiring)
        - MOD src/solutions/WorkspaceLayoutWizard/src/main.tsx (templateFilter query parameter plumbing)

      Build status:
        - SpaarkeAi: PASS (`npm run build` — 798 KB gzip, 0 TS errors)
        - WorkspaceLayoutWizard: PASS (`npm run build` — 426 KB gzip, 0 TS errors)

